data.description: This beautiful 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath home has over 3,000 sq. ft. of living space and is situated on 3.5 beautiful acres.  It's country living, yet only 15 minutes from Chillicothe.  This home has living space for everyone.  The main level features a spacious living room, beautiful kitchen with so much character from the stained glass windows and brick wall leading to the dining room that steps out to a maintenance free deck.  Three large bedrooms are on the main level.  The master suite is attached to a beautifully updated bathroom and walk in closet.  The lower level offers the fourth bedroom, a full bath and half bath, and a large recreation and entertaining area that opens onto the covered patio and hot tub, which stays with the property.  There are storage closets throughout the house and a large 2 1/2 car attached garage. In addition, there is a 20x40 detached garage. New electric furnace 2023, new hot water heater 2021.
